        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This massive branch has been cut into a general club shape but still bears several knots and has a number of runes carved along its length. The deflecting branch is a *+2 greater striking greatclub*. On a critical hit, you knock the target prone.",
